===Noun===
'''[[advection]] [[fog]]'''

#{{cattag|physics|meteorology}} A type of [[fog]] caused by the passage of moist air horizontally over a relatively colder surface and the consequent [[cooling]] of that air to below its [[dew point]].

'''advectional'''. Function: ''Adjective''

Source: FM 3-6 '''Field Behavior of NBC Agents'''

